<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="../assets/xml/rss.xsl" media="all"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>写程序的龙龙 (Posts about CAD)</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/</link><description></description><atom:link href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/categories/cad.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 04 Nov 2017 11:37:32 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>Nikola (getnikola.com)</generator><docs>http://blogs.law.harvard.edu/tech/rss</docs><item><title>CAD练习题7——多边形和圆构成的对称图形</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-7-duo-bian-xing-he-yuan-gou-cheng-de-dui-cheng-tu-xing/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;题目:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p7-4.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p7-4.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这道题没有给中等大小圆的半径，必然要用到三边相切画圆，而给了大圆的直径，必然要用到缩放。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1、构造五边形顶点到对边连线延长线，为三边相切创造条件，进而画出中等大小圆。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p7-1.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p7-1.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2、重复利用三边相切完成图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p7-2.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p7-2.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3、缩放并清理图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p7-3.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p7-3.PNG"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>CAD</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-7-duo-bian-xing-he-yuan-gou-cheng-de-dui-cheng-tu-xing/</guid><pubDate>Sat, 04 Nov 2017 11:33:01 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CAD练习题6——已知圆心及所在直线和圆上的一条弦长画圆，画指定角度和长度的弦</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-6-yi-zhi-yuan-xin-suo-zai-zhi-xian-he-yi-tiao-xian-chang-hua-yuan-hua-zhi-ding-jiao-du-he-chang-du-de-xian/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;题目:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p6-10.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p6-10.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这道题的难点主要有两个：已知圆心及所在直线和圆上的一条弦长，如何画圆；如何画一条指定角度和长度的弦。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1、明显可画的部分比较少。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p6-1.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p6-1.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2、因为已知弦长，所以利用平移二分之一弦长的方法，将圆心所在直线向两侧平移。即可得到圆上两点。类似的方法还可以用在角平分线环境中。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p6-2.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p6-2.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3、在外部作一个等大的圆，画一条指定长度的水平弦，作图方法和上一步类似。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p6-3.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p6-3.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4、旋转上一步的圆到指定角度。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p6-4.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p6-4.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;5、移动外部圆，使得两圆重合，这道题的难点就解决了。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p6-5.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p6-5.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;6、作等分。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p6-6.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p6-6.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;7、清理图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p6-7.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p6-7.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;8、作右侧的对称部分。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p6-8.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p6-8.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;9、清理图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p6-9.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p6-9.PNG"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>CAD</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-6-yi-zhi-yuan-xin-suo-zai-zhi-xian-he-yi-tiao-xian-chang-hua-yuan-hua-zhi-ding-jiao-du-he-chang-du-de-xian/</guid><pubDate>Sat, 04 Nov 2017 11:21:44 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CAD练习题5——连续圆弧的画法</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-5-lian-xu-yuan-hu-de-hua-fa/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;题目:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p5-8.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p5-8.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这道题看上去很乱，大部分都可以慢慢画出来，主要需要留意的是右侧上下对称的连续圆弧。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1、先把明显的地方画好。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p5-1.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p5-1.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2、处理上边的小圆。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p5-2.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p5-2.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3、留意到，中间小圆与上边小圆连线为半径画的圆，正好是”蚕豆“中间的参考线。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p5-3.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p5-3.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4、相切相切半径画出整个“蚕豆”图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p5-4.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p5-4.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;5、处理右侧简单部分。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p5-5.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p5-5.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;6、处理连续圆弧，而连续圆弧的定位，靠的是与半径82.6圆的相切，现有条件下，如果没有这个相切，连续圆弧无法定位。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p5-6.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p5-6.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;7、清理图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p5-7.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p5-7.PNG"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>CAD</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-5-lian-xu-yuan-hu-de-hua-fa/</guid><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2017 13:54:29 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CAD练习题4——平行、垂直于切点的半径、相切相切半径画圆</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-4-ping-xing-chui-zhi-yu-qie-dian-de-ban-jing-xiang-qie-xiang-qie-ban-jing-hua-yuan/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;题目:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p4-6.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p4-6.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这道题给了很多条件，大部分地方都比较容易，需要处理的是左边的40度和右边的80度，左边的40度可以利用平行来做，右边的80度可以利用垂直于切点的半径来做。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1、先把明显的部分画出来。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p4-1.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p4-1.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2、利用平行找角度。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p4-2.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p4-2.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3、相切相切半径画圆。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p4-3.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p4-3.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4、利用垂直于切点的半径做固定角度的切线。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p4-4.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p4-4.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;5、完成图形，清理图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p4-5.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p4-5.PNG"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>CAD</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-4-ping-xing-chui-zhi-yu-qie-dian-de-ban-jing-xiang-qie-xiang-qie-ban-jing-hua-yuan/</guid><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2017 11:12:52 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CAD练习题3——顶点到对边垂线、三边相切画圆、缩放、阵列</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-3-ding-dian-dao-dui-bian-chui-xian-san-bian-xiang-qie-hua-yuan-suo-fang/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;题目:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p3-5.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p3-5.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这道题只给了一个100，其他的条件都不明确。像这样的对称图形，都应优先考虑多边形的使用，再加上一圈都有圆弧相切，应能想到利用相切画圆，又由于无法确定半径，所以肯定要构造三边相切画圆。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1、因为是七个花瓣，所以画一个七边形，利用顶点到对边垂线，构造三边相切画圆。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p3-1.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p3-1.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2、利用镜像或者阵列，得到一圈图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p3-2.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p3-2.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3、清理图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p3-3.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p3-3.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4、画中心的圆，连接垂线，缩放图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p3-4.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p3-4.PNG"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>CAD</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-3-ding-dian-dao-dui-bian-chui-xian-san-bian-xiang-qie-hua-yuan-suo-fang/</guid><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2017 10:28:45 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CAD练习题2——圆心所在直线、镜像、三点画弧、等分、阵列</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-2-yuan-xin-suo-zai-zhi-xian-jing-xiang-san-dian-hua-hu-deng-fen/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;题目:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p2-5.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p2-5.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这道题给了圆心所在的直线，给了圆弧过的两个点，那么如何画出这个弧呢？我们利用的是镜像和三点画弧。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1、画出基本图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p2-1.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p2-1.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2、因为给定了圆心所在的直线，所以可以利用镜像构造三点画弧。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p2-2.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p2-2.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3、利用阵列，画出其他部分。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p2-3.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p2-3.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4、清理图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p2-4.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p2-4.PNG"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>CAD</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-2-yuan-xin-suo-zai-zhi-xian-jing-xiang-san-dian-hua-hu-deng-fen/</guid><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2017 10:11:57 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CAD练习题1——平行、偏移、移动</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-1-ping-xing-pian-yi-yi-dong/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;题目:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p1-6.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p1-6.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这道题主要涉及到平行、偏移和移动，三个主要的工具。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1、利用平行，画出部分已知图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p1-1.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p1-1.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2、因为没法直接连上，先在旁边画上其他已知图形，找找机会。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p1-2.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p1-2.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3、图中的106是连接两个图形的关键点，另外就是图中蓝色的垂线，这条垂线给定了偏移距离。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p1-3.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p1-3.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4、偏移左边图形顶端线，与106水平线交于一点，这个点就是右边图形要移动到的目标点，移动图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p1-4.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p1-4.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;5、去掉多余的线，得到结果。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p1-5.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p1-5.PNG"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>CAD</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-1-ping-xing-pian-yi-yi-dong/</guid><pubDate>Wed, 01 Nov 2017 12:33:23 GMT</pubDate></item></channel></rss>